00:11:01.318 --> 00:11:05.071
Kung talagang magpakita si Prinsesa Huan Zhu, panalo ako,

00:11:05.157 --> 00:11:06.334
at itong jade pendant ay magiging akin.

00:11:09.258 --> 00:11:10.434
Kung matatalo ka,

00:11:13.400 --> 00:11:15.256
Sisiguraduhin kong mamamatay kang walang libingan.

00:11:17.517 --> 00:11:18.630
Deal.

